David Lander https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Lander 0 David Leonard Lander (born June 22, 1947) is an American actor, voice actor, comedian, composer, musician, and baseball scout. He has also worked as the Goodwill Ambassador for the National Multiple Sclerosis Society. He is best known for his portrayal of Squiggy on the sitcom Laverne Shirley. He is the father of Natalie Lander. David_Leonard_Lander ( born June_22_,_1947 ) is an_American_actor , voice_actor , comedian , composer , musician , and baseball_scout .
